## Workers por Analítico

| Worker | Fila consumida | Modelo | Escalável? |
|---|---|---|---|
| `yolo-worker` | `ai.frame` | YOLOv8n (GPU) | ✅ replicas |
| `worker-object-detection` | `ai.detect.object_detection` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ replicas |
| `worker-crowd` | `ai.detect.crowd` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-intrusion` | `ai.detect.intrusion` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-loitering` | `ai.detect.loitering` | nenhum (CPU, stateful) | ⚠️ consistente por camera |
| `worker-abandoned-object` | `ai.detect.abandoned_object` | nenhum (CPU, stateful) | ⚠️ |
| `worker-queue` | `ai.detect.queue` | nenhum (CPU, stateful) | ⚠️ |
| `worker-heatmap` | `ai.detect.heatmap` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-line-crossing` | `ai.detect.line_crossing` | nenhum (CPU, stateful) | ⚠️ |
| `worker-vehicle-traffic` | `ai.detect.vehicle_traffic` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-human-traffic` | `ai.detect.human_traffic` | nenhum (CPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-facial` | `ai.frame.facial` | InsightFace (GPU) | ✅ |
| `worker-lpr` | `ai.frame.lpr` | YOLO plates + OCR | ✅ (fase final) |

> [!NOTE]
> Workers **stateful** (loitering, abandoned, queue, line_crossing) mantêm estado por `camera_id`. Com múltiplas réplicas, o frame-grabber precisa garantir que o mesmo `camera_id` sempre vai para a mesma réplica (consistent hashing).

